{"tid":2072418,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"武肺吹哨人李文亮微博超100萬條悼念留言全數被清空，網民抗議後又被恢復","createTime":"2020-06-20T14:46:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T15:58:25.000Z","uid":48040,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"54e1476e166d432ba27a2e2b06792b5afd80eed5","tid":2072418,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T14:46:56.000Z","msg":"因在社交媒體向親友披露新冠肺炎疫情暴發的的武漢市中心醫院眼科醫生李文亮，不幸在患病後於今年2月7日離世。而他生前發出的最後一則微博帖文的留言區，已累積超過100萬條評論。不少人以在他微博下面留言的方式來表達個人情感和追思，更有人稱其為&ldquo;中國哭牆&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n但在6月19日，有人發現這則帖文的評論突然被全數清空，亦無法再發布評論。事件隨即引起中國大陸網民地不滿和抗議。而經記者最新複查顯示，不久前還消失的評論區最終&ldquo;神奇&rdquo;恢復，不過最多人點贊的熱門評論未顯示在前排，所有評論只能按時間順序排列。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://rfi.my/65qT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frfi.my%2F65qT&d=KvAiISINul4H2q03UsPdudiuVIf%2Fu6affRELz7PmdGA%3D&h=ca7f1f63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rfi.my/65qT</a><br />\n<br />\n=======<br />\nTwitter戰線：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SomethinkMore/status/1274346610307158016?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSomethinkMore%2Fstatus%2F1274346610307158016%3Fs%3D20&d=KvAiISINul4H2q03UsPdudiuVIf%2Fu6affRELz7PmdGA%3D&h=0e581579\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSomethinkMore%2Fstatus%2F1274346610307158016%3Fs%3D20&h=2394b811\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SomethinkMore/status/1274346610307158016?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n支持我地：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/somethink\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fsomethink&d=KvAiISINul4H2q03UsPdudiuVIf%2Fu6affRELz7PmdGA%3D&h=32858db8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/somethink</a>"},{"pid":"8e8eb46e00fccac500c249c95af85cd8e18a5f64","tid":2072418,"uid":91519,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T14:47:51.000Z","msg":"連悼念都不允許<br />\n香港都就快"},{"pid":"4cc596979fbaa0d5c3d59d1c7d5eb1cf77e96c66","tid":2072